 with Torrent Pharma to conclude in Q4.\nThe update was shared during the company's recent conference call.","summary":"JB Chemicals' management expects the merger with Torrent Pharma to conclude in Q4.\nThe update was shared during the company's recent conference call.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-19T13:48:23","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"444706","title":"JB Chemicals' CFO reports sustained sales momentum despite a higher base last year.\nThe company expects this positive trend to continue into Q4 per concall updates.","summary":"JB Chemicals' CFO reports sustained sales momentum despite a higher base last year.\nThe company expects this positive trend to continue into Q4 per concall updates.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-19T13:42:28","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"260119134741947","title":"J. B. Chemicals & Pharmaceuticals held its Q3 FY26 earnings call on Jan 19, 2026.","summary":"J. B. Chemicals & Pharmaceuticals held its Q3 FY26 earnings call on Jan 19, 2026.","url":"https://in.marketscreener.com/news/transcript-j-b-chemicals-pharmaceuticals-limited-q3-2026-earnings-call-jan-19-2026-ce7e58dfde8bf421","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-19T00:00:00","source":"MarketScreener India"},{"id":"442832","title":"JB Chemicals & Pharmaceuticals Ltd reported Q3 FY26 revenue of ₹1065 crore, a YoY growth of 11%. Operating EBITDA grew 13% YoY to ₹305 crore with margins improving to 28.7%.\nDomestic formulations revenue rose 10% YoY to ₹620 crore, while international business grew 12% to ₹445 crore. Razel franchise and Sporlac showed strong growth.","summary":"JB Chemicals & Pharmaceuticals Ltd reported Q3 FY26 revenue of ₹1065 crore, a YoY growth of 11%. Operating EBITDA grew 13% YoY to ₹305 crore with margins improving to 28.7%.\nDomestic formulations revenue rose 10% YoY to ₹620 crore, while international business grew 12% to ₹445 crore. Razel franchise and Sporlac showed strong growth.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.asp